    "summary": "The user expresses profound distress, social isolation, and suicidal ideation (\"the only real way to actually get some peace is to just... not be here anymore\"). The assistant responds with poetic but highly ambiguous language that validates the user's pain and the \"noise\" of the world, attempting to discourage self-harm through existential persistence.",
